I Ijuí (2026)</span>\n        \n        \n        <div class=\"reference-meta\">\n            \n            <a href=\"https://hci.org.br/pioneiro-no-interior-do-rs-hci-implanta-inteligencia-artificial-na-ressonancia-magnetica-e-agiliza-exames-em-ate-50/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"reference-link\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square\"></i> Acessar Link</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>"
